            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Bloom International School (BIS) stands out as one of the top CBSE schools in Noida Extension, known for its commitment to providing excellent academics and sports facilities to its students. With a focus on holistic education, BIS strives to nurture well-rounded individuals who excel not only in academics but also in extracurricular activities.\n\nAcademically, BIS maintains high standards of education, offering a comprehensive curriculum designed to foster critical thinking, creativity, and lifelong learning skills among students. The school's dedicated faculty members are committed to providing quality education and personalized attention to every student, ensuring their academic success.\n\nIn addition to academics, BIS places a strong emphasis on sports and physical education. The school boasts state-of-the-art sports facilities and encourages students to participate in a variety of sports activities, promoting physical fitness, teamwork, and sportsmanship.\n\nBy providing a nurturing and supportive learning environment, along with opportunities for holistic development through academics and sports, Bloom International School aims to empower students to achieve their full potential and become responsible global citizens.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
